.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-AGE-SKEWNESS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-age-skewness \- FEAT-3646 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-age-skewness
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the skewness of peer age in seconds across all connected peers (FEAT-3646).
.PP
Output: JSON with key age_skewness_peer.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
